translations.Action required: Your ownCloud user limi: Action requerido our ownCloud usuario limit has been exceeded
translations.User limit exceeded. To add more users c: usuario limit exceeded. To agregar mas users click here
translations.To add or enable additional users, pleas: To agregar or activar adicional users, Por favor see https://software.qnap.com/owncloud.html for your licensing opciones.
translations.ownCloud for QNAP comes as Community Edi: ownCloud for QNAP comes as comunidad Edition by default and is free to usar for up to 5 users.
translations.If you need more than 5 users or want to: If tú need mas than 5 users or want to usar any of our Enterprise aplicaciones from the mercado, tú need to upgrade to Enterprise Edition by purchasing licenses from the QNAP Software Store.
translations.Guest users don't count as normal users,: Invitado users don't count as normal users, That means tú can invite as many as needed.
